Section 1:
Act 872 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas As Engrossed: H4/7/25
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1106
4
5 By: Joint Budget Committee
6
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO MAKE AN APPROPRIATION FOR PERSONAL
10 SERVICES, OPERATING EXPENSES AND DATA PROCESSING
11 SYSTEM/SERVICES FOR THE OFFICE OF THE TREASURER OF
12 STATE FOR THE FISCAL YEAR ENDING JUNE 30, 2026; AND
13 FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
14
15
Subtitle
16
17 AN ACT FOR THE OFFICE OF THE TREASURER
18 OF STATE APPROPRIATION FOR THE 2025-2026
19 FISCAL YEAR.
20
21
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
23
24 SECTION 1. REGULAR SALARIES - OPERATIONS. There is hereby established
25 for the Office of the Treasurer of State for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the
26 following maximum number of regular employees.
