17 (22) Q094U TREAS ASSISTANT III 3 GRADE SGS04
18 (23) Q085U TREAS ASSISTANT II 4 GRADE SGS04
19 MAX. NO. OF EMPLOYEES 33
20
21 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - OPERATIONS. There is hereby authorized, for
22 the Office of the Treasurer of State for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the
23 following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be known as
24 "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such purposes: five
25 (5) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to
26 exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or
27 its successor, or this act for the appropriate classification.
28
29 SECTION 3. APPROPRIATION - OPERATIONS. There is hereby appropriated,
30 to the Office of the Treasurer of State, to be payable from the State Central
31 Services Fund, for personal services, operating expenses, data processing
32 system/services, debt collection and Financial/Educational Programs including
33 the Arkansas 529 College Savings Program, Arkansas ABLE Program and financial
34 education of the Office of the Treasurer of State for the fiscal year ending
35 June 30, 2026, the following:
36
